      <title>Niche blogging an easy way to make money</title>
      <link>http://dollarjames.com/niche-blogging-an-easy-way-to-make-money</link>
      <comments>http://dollarjames.com/niche-blogging-an-easy-way-to-make-money#comments</comments>
