      <description>Do you want to make money online ? I know how to, and I can help you! This is no BS, what I am offering is something real which I am going to explain right now. The idea came to me today while I was surfing on searchengineland.com.
As you know I can easily make money [...]&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;SHARETHIS.addEntry({ title: "Make Money Online with me!", url: "http://dollarjames.com/make-money-online-with-me" });&lt;/script&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/dollar-james-/Dollar_James_-Make_Money_Online_with_me.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;">Do you want to <strong>make money online</strong> ? I know how to, and I can help you! This is no BS, what I am offering is something real which I am going to explain right now. The idea came to me today while I was surfing on <a title="Search Engine Land" href="http://www.searchengineland.com" target="_blank">searchengineland.com</a>.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">As you know I can easily make money online with websites on <strong>niche markets</strong>. I actually make between €30 and €120 euros per month on some of my websites and regularly receive Google <strong>Adsense</strong> cheques. Meanwhile I would really like to make even more money. For this I need to have more time, which I dont have unfortunately and which is the reason why I dont have so much time to write on my blog lately.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Today I had this bright idea. I know how to find niche markets, I know SEO as its my job, I know how to get popular, I know how to turn my website in something profitable, BUT I want to make even more money. I have actually found how, and guess what ? You will <strong>make money online with m</strong>e also!!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Yes its by working with you readers and webmasters that it will work. By sharing our work and knowledge all together we will all make money together. The concept is quite simple. I will do part of the work, by finding niche markets for us. I will create my website on a particular niche market to show you how to optimize it for SEO (which keywords &amp; best practices) and to show you what sort of template to use. For example, when I use a template like <a title="Zyoptix Lasik surgery" href="http://www.zyoptixlaser.com" target="_blank">Zyoptix Laser eye surgery</a> I can get a very high CTR. You will also therefore have some quality content in order to understand what the niche is about. Once this is done, I will submit the niche market to the people following me on my twitter account (DollarJames), so that they can start creating websites on that same niche. Together we will be able to create a network of websites on the same topic. We can do linking, which is good for SEO, we can exchange websites where we can get backlinks. All of this all together!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Doing this will enable our websites to become popular very quickly by being well ranked in Google. Furthermore, a buzz could be created around our websites and how much money we are making with them. And the more traffic we have the more money we will make as I will help you have a good CTR.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Post a comment if you are willing to make money with me, and add me on Twitter, my username is &#8220;DollarJames&#8221;.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><p>Technorati Tags: <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/make+money+online+with+me" rel="tag">make money online with me</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/adsense" rel="tag"> adsense</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/seo" rel="tag"> seo</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/trafic" rel="tag"> trafic</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/twitter" rel="tag"> twitter</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/niche+dollarjames" rel="tag"> niche dollarjames</a></p>
