      <description>While surfing today on Rajaie Talks blog, I saw one of his articles about a project launched by Gyutae Park from Winning The Web. The project is in fact a ranking of the Top Internet Marketing blogs. Of course, being curious I went and had a look. I was quickly suprised to see that the [...]&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;SHARETHIS.addEntry({ title: "Top Internet Marketing Blogs", url: "http://dollarjames.com/top-internet-marketing-blogs" });&lt;/script&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/dollar-james-/Dollar_James_-Top_Internet_Marketing_Blogs.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;">While surfing today on <a title="Rajaie Talks Blog" href="http://www.rajaietalks.com/top-internet-marketing-blogs" target="_blank">Rajaie Talks blog</a>, I saw one of his articles about a project launched by Gyutae Park from <a title="Winning the Web" href="http://www.winningtheweb.com" target="_blank">Winning The Web</a>. The project is in fact a ranking of the <strong><a title="WTW Top Internet Marketing Blogs" href="http://www.winningtheweb.com/im-top-blogs/" target="_blank">Top Internet Marketing blogs</a></strong>. Of course, being curious I went and had a look. I was quickly suprised to see that the ranking is in fact very reliable and that it is therefore a great source to find quality blogs to go and visit.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">What can really be appreciated is that the ranking takes into consideration several reliable elements: the number of RSS subscribers, Alexa ranking, Compete rankings, Technorati rankings but also the Google Page rank, number of inbound links, the number of stumble upon reviews, the amount of del.icio.us saves and the amount of backlinks. From these elements, points are awarded to the blogs in order to have a ranking. As you can see it is an extremely complete and accurate ranking.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.winningtheweb.com/im-top-blogs/"><img class="aligncenter" title="Top Internet Marketing blogs" src="http://www.rajaietalks.com/wp-content/uploads/topblogs.png" alt="Top Internet Marketing blogs" width="500" height="230" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Unfortunately Dollar James being only a Google page rank 2, I am not yet in the ranking. Meanwhile with a continuous work, I should be able to improve significantly my various rankings. My strategy for the moment is to focus on link building, and as you may imagine, I will definitely use these Top Internet Marketing Blogs in order to get useful information but probably also a few backlinks.</p>
