    <item>
      <title>Adsense Revenue Update</title>
      <link>http://dollarjames.com/adsense-revenue-update</link>
      <comments>http://dollarjames.com/adsense-revenue-update#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Dec 2008 23:35:26 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>James</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Adsense]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[adsense blogs]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[make money online]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[revenue]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://dollarjames.com/?p=116</guid>
      <description>Just wanted to inform update you about how I make money online, and how much I make. So basically, I make money by writing blogs about topics I know about.  In the last two months, I safely received 2 cheques from Google. For september, I received a $213 cheque where as for october I received [...]&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;SHARETHIS.addEntry({ title: "Adsense Revenue Update", url: "http://dollarjames.com/adsense-revenue-update" });&lt;/script&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/dollar-james-/Dollar_James_-Adsense_Revenue_Update.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: justify;">Just wanted to inform update you about how I <strong>make money online</strong>, and how much I make. So basically, I make money by writing blogs about topics I know about.  In the last two months, I safely received 2 cheques from Google. For september, I received a $213 cheque where as for october I received a $131 cheque. So which blog performed well?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The blogs that performed well were as usual &#8220;<a title="The Color Contacts Guide" href="http://thecolorcontacts.blogspot.com" target="_blank">The Color Contacts</a>&#8221; which made between $70 to $80 each month. <a title="My Color Contacts Blog" href="http://mycolorcontacts.blogspot.com" target="_blank">My color contacts</a> blog made between $15 and $25 in the month. Regarding my two eye laser blogs, Eye Laser Surgery &amp; Lasix Surgery blog, the earnings were also around $20 each. My others blogs making the remaing dollars. As you may have noticed i have removed adsense from <strong>Dollar James</strong> for the moment.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">If you have read recently my last articles, you may have noticed that I have launched several blogs in the last week in order to talk about topics I know about but also to analyse the impact of a domain name on the Google Ranking. I have therefore launched 3 blogs about handhelds pda &amp; <a title="Smartphone Nokia E71 Review" href="http://handheldspda.com/smartphone-nokia-e71" target="_blank">smartphones</a>. They are <a title="Handhelds PDA Guide" href="http://handheldspda.com" target="_blank">Handhelds PDA</a> which is hosted on DollarJames, <a title="PDA Handhelds Guide" href="http://www.pda-handhelds.com" target="_blank">PDA Handhelds</a> &amp; <a title="Handhelds Computers Guide" href="http://www.handheldscomputers.com" target="_blank">Handhelds Computers</a> which are hosted on Blogger but have their own domain name. I have also launched an extra blog on <a title="Eyes Surgery Guide" href="http://www.eyes-surgery.com" target="_blank">eye laser surgery</a> with a proper domain name in order to have a better visibility in Google and therefore to have more readers.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Regarding this month, my earnings will be again around $130, even though I hope that with the new blogs, it will increase to around $200 considering it is christmas also! As usual I will keep you updated in the next months!</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><p>Technorati Tags: <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/adsense" rel="tag">adsense</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/revenue" rel="tag"> revenue</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/adsense+blogs" rel="tag"> adsense blogs</a>, <a href="http://technorati.com/tag/make+money+online" rel="tag"> make money online</a></p>
